::'''Wen Shiqi:''' IPC? Let me remind you, I'm a Lv. 2 researcher at the Department of Implement Arts, okay? Level 2! Can you even comprehend how much a Lv. 2 researcher is worth? I'm just handling the internal purchase system for space station staff.
::'''Wen Shiqi:''' Can't help it. No rest for the capable. I'm notoriously popular around the Department of Implement Arts, so everyone leaves the important job of liaising with the IPC over to me!
