:{{DIcon|Talk}} Internal purchase system? What's that?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011521-->
::'''Wen Shiqi:''' You've come to the right place. That's my line of work. Just as the name suggests, it's a purchase system subcontracted to the IPC that's only available for space station staff.
::'''Wen Shiqi:''' There's some pretty cool and useful stuff in there, especially if you're doing research. It's just... The only currency it accepts at the moment is Hertareum.
::'''Wen Shiqi:''' And it's an exclusive supply, if you get my drift... The whole thing is designed to recycle Hertareum. You can't actually say that to anyone, though.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
